  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a deep frying pan to 350 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "In a shallow dish, mix together the flour, cornstarch, smoked paprika, garlic powder, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Dredge the Australian green olives in the flour mixture, shaking off excess.",
    "Roll the floured olives in the vegan panko breadcrumbs to coat.",
    "Deep-fry the breaded olives in batches until golden brown, about 2-3 minutes per batch.",
    "Drain the fried olives on paper towels.",
    "Arrange the fried olives in a hot dolsot stone bowl.",
    "Drizzle the lemon juice over the fried olives.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy."
